description:
Extend the DevFlow Zustand store with Beads integration state:

```typescript
beadsIntegration: {
  isConnected: boolean;
  dbPath: string | null;
  readyIssues: Issue[];
  allIssues: Issue[];
  selectedIssueId: string | null;
  filters: BeadsFilters;
}
```

Actions:
- `setBeadsConnection`
- `setReadyIssues`
- `setAllIssues`
- `setSelectedIssue`
- `updateBeadsFilters`
- `upsertBeadsIssue` (for real-time updates)
